title: Nearby the beach
text: A wonderful stay at Camelia Studios by the sunny Crete Beach. Very hot during night time. Even hotter at daytime. But when only 10-15 meter close to the sandy beach, it doesn't matter. Some noice from wild MC bikers.

title: Smooth and relaxed
text: You hardly notice any problem travelling a well smoothed airline - as experienced by my last SAS travel t/r Alicante

title: Fresh and spicy
text: Looking for an excellent cuisine? Try little India and get a diffent view of downtown restaurants in Skien

title: Highlighted Acropolis
text: Highlight your stay at Acropolis by strolling around in the old Plaka and even visit the harbour in Pireus

title: A must for travellers
text: The historic waterway of industralisation - and should be a part of the UNESCO status of Rjukan and Notodden.

title: Jazzfest Skien
text: An incredible festival of mostly local and internationally known jazz players, among Lage Lund, Gard Nilssen, Bugge Wesseltoft and Scheen Jazzorkester

title: Culinaire experience
text: As allways an culinaire experience - Indian food at the very best. But ask for better spice as here they are very adjusted to a norwegian low level of spice

title: Best view of Oslo seaside
text: At sealevel - experience the sun going down over the skyline of Oslo. Maybe the best and at the same time the most hidden place. Reachable by a regular timescheduled ferry.

title: Alhambra - looking toward Sierra Nevada
text: Alhambra - also named as The red Castle - is a palace and fortress build in the middle of 1300th. Today listed at UNESCO's list of heritage.

title: A high class stay at budget.
text:
The owner Marcel understand that guests is The Core as a weldriven hotel. He takes time to talk to each guest. The rooms are so clean that we commented it. Just outtside
there is a smal swimming pool. The hotel is situated in the upper town and gives you a quiet and calm atmosphere.

title: Lamb dish - but could actually be anything
text: Micro-owen heated prefabricated food at not even tasteful shape. Friendly service of two thai ladies.
